    <item>
      <title>英国板球的抛售赌博使球队价值超过 10 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/english-cricket-s-selloff-gamble-values-teams-at-over-1-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一场拍卖会将八支英格兰板球队估价近 10 亿英镑（13 亿美元），这对于四年前才成立的英格兰最新板球赛事来说是一个巨大成功。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/english-cricket-s-selloff-gamble-values-teams-at-over-1-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
